---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <canvas class="hero-net" id="heroNet" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-text reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow on-dark">LOGICCRAFT · 사고력 EdTech 스튜디오</p>
          <h1>생각하는 힘을 키우는 <em>제품</em>을 만듭니다.</h1>
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a href="/apps" class="btn btn-primary">제품 보기 <span class="arr">→</span></a>
            <a href="/about" class="btn btn-ghost">스튜디오 소개</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-art reveal">
          <div class="mascot-float">
            <div class="mascot-panel" id="mascotPanel">
              <div class="glare"></div>
              <div class="mascot-row">
                <img class="naru" src="/mascots/naru.png" alt="나루 — 아기 비버 마스코트" />
                <img class="neti" src="/mascots/neti.png" alt="느티 — 새싹 정령 마스코트" />
              </div>
              <div class="mascot-caption">
                <div class="m"><b>나루</b><span>NARU</span></div>
                <div class="m"><b>느티</b><span>NETI</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ SYNERGEION ============ -->
  <section class="synergeion" id="synergeion">
    <div class="wrap syn-grid">
      <div class="syn-copy reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">SYNERGEION · 대표 시리즈</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">3세부터 18세까지,<br />하나의 여정으로 이어집니다.</h2>
        <a href="/synergeion" class="btn btn-dark">시리즈 자세히 보기 <span class="arr">→</span></a>
      </div>
      <div class="journey reveal">
        <div class="spine"><div class="spine-fill" id="spineFill"></div></div>
        <div class="stage" style="--st: var(--st-wonder)">
          <span class="num">01</span>
          <div class="body"><h4>Wonder <span class="age">3–6세</span></h4><p>새싹을 길러 자라는 걸 관찰합니다.</p></div>
          <span class="tag live">출시</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stage" style="--st: var(--st-build)">
          <span class="num">02</span>
          <div class="body"><h4>Build <span class="age">6–9세</span></h4><p>그 나무로 집과 배를 만듭니다.</p></div>
          <span class="tag dev">개발 중</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stage" style="--st: var(--st-voyage)">
          <span class="num">03</span>
          <div class="body"><h4>Voyage <span class="age">9–12세</span></h4><p>그 배를 타고 새 땅을 찾아 나섭니다.</p></div>
          <span class="tag dev">개발 중</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stage" style="--st: var(--st-forge)">
          <span class="num">04</span>
          <div class="body"><h4>Forge <span class="age">12–15세</span></h4><p>직접 벼린 도구로 자기만의 집을 짓습니다.</p></div>
          <span class="tag soon">예정</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stage" style="--st: var(--st-village)">
          <span class="num">05</span>
          <div class="body"><h4>Village <span class="age">15–18세</span></h4><p>여러 사람과 모여 사는 마을을 짓습니다.</p></div>
          <span class="tag soon">예정</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ PRODUCTS ============ -->
  <section class="products" id="products">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">PRODUCTS · 우리가 만든 도구</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 교육 -->
      <div class="section-block" style="margin-top: clamp(40px,5vw,64px)">
        <div class="cat-head reveal">
          <span class="label">교육</span>
          <span class="rule"></span>
          <span class="count">04</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid">

          <!-- Featured: Wonder -->
          <article class="pcard feature reveal">
            <div class="feat-art">
              <div class="feat-mascots">
                <img src="/mascots/naru.png" alt="나루 마스코트" />
                <img class="neti" src="/mascots/neti.png" alt="느티 마스코트" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feat-body">
              <p class="eyebrow warm">SYNERGEION 시리즈 · 출시</p>
              <div class="name-row"><h3>Synergeion Wonder</h3><span class="chip">3–6세</span></div>
              <p class="desc">아이와 부모가 함께 자라는 사고력 정원. 매일 씨앗 한 알, 부모도 같이 자랍니다.</p>
              <div class="links">
                <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/synergeion-wonder/id6774041352">App Store</a>
                <a class="muted" href="/apps/wonder/support">지원</a>
                <a class="muted" href="/apps/wonder/privacy">개인정보</a>
                <a class="muted" href="/apps/wonder/terms">약관</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/robotrail.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>로보트레일</h3><span class="chip">컴퓨팅 사고력</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">코드 없이 로봇을 움직이며 코딩 사고력을 훈련하는 퍼즐 앱.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/id6764465655">App Store</a>
              <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.smartsikhye.robotrail">Google Play</a>
              <a class="muted" href="https://woosiq92.github.io/robotrail/support.html">지원</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/science-club.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>과학자 클럽</h3><span class="chip">과학</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">추측·발견·분기·회고 4단계로 매일 한 별씩 켜는 과학 사고 게임.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/id6771675434">App Store</a>
              <a class="muted" href="https://woosiq92.github.io/science-club/privacy.html">개인정보</a>
              <a class="muted" href="https://woosiq92.github.io/science-club/terms.html">약관</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/scienceapp.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>왜 그렇게 생각해?</h3><span class="chip">융합 사고력</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">정답이 아니라 답에 도달하는 사고 과정을 9과목으로 훈련하는 자기주도 학습 플랫폼(웹).</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://logicschool.co.kr">바로가기 →</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 일상 -->
      <div class="section-block">
        <div class="cat-head daily reveal">
          <span class="label">일상</span>
          <span class="rule"></span>
          <span class="count">03</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid">
          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/ourfootprint.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>커플맵로그</h3><span class="chip warm">지도</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">둘이 다녀온 동네가 색으로 칠해지는 커플 데이트 점령 지도.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/id6769797672">App Store</a>
              <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.logiccraft.ourfootprint">Google Play</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/ourfootprint/support">지원</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/ourfootprint/privacy">개인정보</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/stockwatch.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>불안한개미</h3><span class="chip warm">주식 시세</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">매매 없이 시세만 — 거치대·위젯·잠금화면으로 보는 한국 주식 시세.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/id6772662894">App Store</a>
              <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.logiccraft.stockwatch">Google Play</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/stockwatch/support">지원</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/stockwatch/privacy">개인정보</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="pcard reveal">
            <div class="top">
              <img class="icon" src="/icons/sedolal.png" alt="" />
              <div><div class="name-row"><h3>세상돌아가는거알아버리기</h3><span class="chip warm">시사·사회</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <p class="desc">정치 몰라도 OK. 친구처럼 알려주는 정치·시사 한 토막과 우리 동네 후보·의원 정리.</p>
            <div class="links">
              <a href="https://apps.apple.com/kr/app/id6770908480">App Store</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/sedolal/support">지원</a>
              <a class="muted" href="/apps/sedolal/privacy">개인정보</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ MEDIA + BOOK ============ -->
  <section class="media-band">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="reveal" style="margin-bottom: 30px">
        <p class="eyebrow">MORE · 영상과 글</p>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="color:#fff">제품 너머의 이야기.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="media-grid">
        <a class="tile youtube reveal" href="https://www.youtube.com/@logiccraftmovie">
          <div class="yt-mark"></div>
          <h3>로직크래프트 YouTube</h3>
          <p class="handle">@logiccraftmovie</p>
          <p>제품 이야기와 사고력 콘텐츠를 영상으로 만나보세요.</p>
          <span class="go">채널 보기 <span class="arr">→</span></span>
        </a>
        <a class="tile book reveal" href="https://product.kyobobook.co.kr/detail/S000219252300">
          <div class="book-cover">
            <img src="/book-cover.jpg" alt="당연함을 의심하는 연습 표지" onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';" />
            <div class="cover-fallback" style="display:none"><b>당연함을<br />의심하는 연습</b><span>최우식 지음</span></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="meta">최우식 지음 · 수필·자기계발 · 2026 · 132쪽</p>
            <h3>당연함을 의심하는 연습</h3>
            <p>자기·사랑·사회·일상·배움 — 5가지 영역의 당연함을 49편의 짧은 에세이로 의심합니다.</p>
            <span class="go">교보문고에서 보기 <span class="arr">→</span></span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script src="/constellation.js" is:inline></script>
</Layout>
